            {
                "comment": "I really enjoyed learning from Dr. Wolman! You could tell that he really has a passion for genetics and that he wants to see his students succeed.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "He explains difficult concepts so well, and helps solidify content with a little review before lecture (still study up). He goes a little fast through content, but comfortable enough where you can keep up in class. Very organized, well spoken, and my favorite of the 151 professors.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
